<p>Ireland stepped out in a pair of slides and wore her blonde hair up in a messy topknot.</p>

<p>The model completed her ensemble with a patterned cloth face mask.</p>

<p>The sighting comes a day after her father and his second wife Hilaria Baldwin welcomed their fifth child.</p>

